        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>This setting can be chosen by the Gamemaster and will be system wide. This setting has four options.</p><p><strong>1. Fourth Edition Step Table (Default)</strong></p><p>For further information please check out the <a href=\"https://earthdawn.fasa.wiki/4E/Systems/Step-and-Action-Table\">FASA wiki page</a></p><p><strong>2. First Edition Step Table</strong></p><p>For further information please check out the <a href=\"https://earthdawn.fasa.wiki/en/4E/Systems/Step-and-Action-Table-1E\">FASA wiki page</a></p><p><strong>3. Third Edition Step Table</strong></p><p>For further information please check out the <a href=\"https://earthdawn.fasa.wiki/en/4E/Systems/Step-and-Action-Table-3E\">FASA wiki page</a></p><p><strong>4. Classic Edition Step Table</strong> </p><p>For further information please check out ??? official page???</p>"
      },
