      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>The Attribute enhancement setting has three options.</p><p><strong>1. Paid enhancement</strong></p><p>this follows the rules on page 447 Players Guide. </p><p><strong>2. One Paid enhancement per circle</strong></p><p>this option follows the first optional rule on page 448 Players Guide</p><p><strong>3. One free enhancement per circle</strong></p><p>this option follows the second optional rule on page 448 Players Guide</p><p></p>"
